REMEMBER THE FOLLOWING RULES: 
1. All requirements below are running totals, inclusive of the levels before them.
 \(e.g. 6,050,000 credits is the absolute max needed for IMP, not 7,150,000\) 
2. Resident access level is required for Military Ships Licence \(still needs +10 reputation as well\). 
3. Citizen access level is required for Advanced Modules Licence \(still needs +20 reputation as well\). 
4. Militia access level is required for Advanced Ships Licence \(still needs +20 reputation as well\). 
5. Most neutral/shipbuilding corporations can sell their licenses directly at high cost, without reputation or citizenship requirements.

IMP -- Galactic Empire
Resident: Production Stations - 1; Credit Transactions - 50,000;
Citizen: Production Stations - 1; Credit Transactions - 1,050,000;
Militia: Production Stations - 2; Credit Transactions - 6,050,000; Frontier Defence Stations - 1;

